				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\mathbf{W}}^{{{\rm{COM}}}}$$\end{document}WCOM. Importantly, the use of data on gross commuting flows at the onset of the COVID-19 outbreak ensures the exogeneity of space–time lags calculated on the basis of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
